  </header>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <main class="container mx-auto flex-1 mt-8 px-6">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 text-gray-800">
      üì¶ Danh s√°ch s·∫£n ph·∫©m
